summary: Hair color and makeup can easily be changed in racemenu. Picked up Helgen keep key from warden's chest. She may not be lore-friendly, but hair color is the only lore-breaker really.
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]She is Imperial race. I simply tweaked the ears in Racemenu. I designed her to my taste but figured someone else might appreciate her beauty. She is my first upload. Haven't given her a name, I figured that should be left up to her player.


[u]WOULD ANYONE BE WILLING TO HELP ME CREATE A FOLLOWER OUT OF HER?

I have pretty much zero mod creation skills. If someone could just create her as a follower and credit me then Iwould be so happy. I'd love to have her as a follower and I had the request made by someone. If she is made into a follower by you just comment or mail me to let me know :D Please and Thank You <3[/u]

[/size]
